    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely dice your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[550ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>green lentils</strong></p>",
