          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1628672601594-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p><p>Combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Wash and dry your<strong> salad</strong>, then add it to the bowl and stir it all together – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p><p>Once golden, remove the <strong>Greek-style aubergine pastitsio bake</strong> from the oven and allow to cool slightly</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
